INSERT INTO `content` (`id`, `parentid`, `content_title`, `sort`, `promo_title`, `promo_text`, `content_text`, `image`, `published`, `externurl`) VALUES (121,49,'Android',2,'Android','<div class=block>Conan Chat for Android </div>\r\n<br><center>\r\n<div  colspan=3 class=download> \r\n<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=100%>\r\n<tr align=center><td><img src=\"/img/platform/android.png\"></td><td><a href=\"market://search?q=pname:darkfactor.conanchat\">Android market :<br> Android 2.1+ ( 0.6.4 - b588 ) </a></td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Android Patchnotes 0.6.0</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.6.0 ( RC : build 394 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- App 2 SD support<br>\r\n- You can now click on chat lines / character in the \"channel\" tab.<br>\r\n- The friends list should not make the application freeze as bad as it used to<br>\r\n- The friends list is now displaying offline characters ( 50 pr  page )<br>\r\n- Added option page<br>\r\n- Tweaked the threshold for when to drop the network connection<br>\r\n- Added reconnect feature ( that can be turned on/off in the option page )<br>\r\n- Fixed a crash<br>\r\n- Added notification on the status bar ( on the homescreen ) when you get messages and the client doesn\"	 have focus.<br>\r\n- Changed the icons on the tabs to be smaller so that the text is easier to read<br>\r\n- You get the \"Copy Text\" option when pressing on a chatline now.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5.2 ( RC : build 255 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Removed the connecting tag on the active character for characterselection.<br>\r\n- Fixed the US connection<br>\r\n- You now get a proper error if you log in to a universe where you have no characters<br>\r\n- Added checkbox to remember password ( default off = does not save the password )<br>\r\n- Added button to see the password in cleartext<br>\r\n- Added button to remove the accountdetails from the account<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5.1 ( RC : build 244 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Fixed an error that occured every time you sent any kind of message.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5 ( RC : build 237 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Can now send tells to ingame characters\r\n<br>\r\n- Added menu when clicking in chatgroups to change group and send tell to a character\r\n<br>\r\n- Added menu in the friendslist to add/remove friends and send them a tel<br>\r\nl\r\n- Added menu in the friendslist to show/hide offline characters<br>\r\n- Added icons to the tabs\r\n- Added optionmenu to disconnect and exit the client in the chatpage<br>\r\n- Added helpwindow ( 1st draft ) that opens the first time you goto the chatpage<br>\r\n\r\n- Fixed the channel/character receiver not working after rotating the phone or putting the app in the background<br>\r\n- Added icon to be able to select receiving group in the channel tab<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.4 ( Beta : build 206 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- Removed the \"add account\" system and changed it so you do a username/password login each time<br>\r\n- Added the rest of the class icons to the character selection screen<br>\r\n- Added the class icons to the friendslist<br>\r\n- Fixed connecting issues<br>\r\n- Fixed network threads not beeing killed when disconnecting a character and you have multiple characters logged in<br>\r\n- Readded the send button since some deviced could not send the message directly from the softkeyboard.<br>\r\n- Started to change the chatwindow ( will be pushed in the next update )<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.3 ( Alpha : build 162 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- Added notifications to the statusbar when receiving messages when the client is in the background<br>\r\n- Tabs will highlight when receiving messages in them and they don\"	 have focus<br>\r\n- Friendslist will only update when the player goes online/offline or levels up now ( not when changing zone )<br